, green thumb or no, is just as fresh and stirring today as then.Full of timeless wit and grace, The Liberty Hyde Bailey Gardener's Companion collects essays and poems from Bailey's many books on gardening, as well as from newspapers and magazines from the era. Whether you've been gardening for decades or are searching for your first inspiration, Bailey's words will make an ideal companion on your journey.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aGardeningvLiterary collections. 0aGardening. 0aGardensvLiterary collections. 0aGardens. 4aGardening & Landscape Design. 4aGeneral Science. 4aNature Guides & Natural History. 7aGARDENING / Essays & Narratives.2bisacsh  aLiberty Hyde Bailey, gardening, environmentalism, philosophy, horticulture, ecology, agricultural journalism.1 aLinstrom, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLinstrom, John, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStempien, John A., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aStempien, John, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065198008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2019 Englishz978311061053608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2019z9783110606386oZDB-23-DPM40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781501740275zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501740275423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/doc